    <p><!--I'm in transition from NYC to the Bay Area. I'm intensely curious, striving to solve design problems with grace & simplicity.-->I'm <a href="portfolio">looking for my next role</a> as a product design director. Currently consulting with <a href="https://www.producthunt.com/posts/shep">Shep</a>; previously at  <a href="https://thoughtbot.com">thoughtbot</a> in SF and<!--<a href="https://www.sesamecare.com">Sesame</a>,<--> <a href="https://www.fjordnet.com">Fjord</a> in NYC<!-- (<a href="https://medium.com/design-voices"> where I created Design Voices</a>, hosted <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/fjord-fika/id1188221550">Fika</a>)--> among others. <!--Don't be a stranger. I write on <a href="https://medium.com/@SkipperWarson">Medium</a>, snap photos on <a href="">Instagram</a>, <a href="https://twitter.com/skippercwarson">tweet some</a>, and rarely go on, if we're being honest, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/skipperchong">LinkedIn</a>--></p>
	<p>In these uncertain times, please let me know if I can be of service to you.</p>
